@Node "Errors"
@Toc "Main"
@Prev "Main"
@Next "Main"
@Title "Explanations/Solutions to various errors"

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Text output to console:
"Cannot find "Sbase4:"
GetSdat 38.126: device (or volume) not mounted" :

Problem  : You need to assign 'Sbase4:'
Solution : Install Sbase4pro 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Requester appearing with error :

Text "Cannot open window" :
Problem  : You are low on memory.
Solution : Free some chipmem !
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Text "Cannot open required library" : 
Problem : You need one/more libraries distributed with WB 3.0 or higher.
Solution : Work with a properly installed workbench !!!
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
@EndNode

